query:
SELECT p.id, p.id_paciente, p.nome, COUNT(a.id) as agendamentos
FROM pacientes p
LEFT JOIN agendamentos a ON a.paciente_id = p.id
WHERE p.tenant_id = 1 
  AND p.id_paciente NOT LIKE 'MIG-%'
  AND p.id_paciente != '2026-0000052'
GROUP BY p.id, p.id_paciente, p.nome
HAVING COUNT(a.id) > 0;
